<h1>Welcome to Black Cat CMS!</h1>

<p><strong>Black Cat CMS</strong> is an Open Source Content Management System (CMS) that allows for
faster and easier management of website content. Black Cat CMS is scalable for small
businesses to large corporations, but is still easy enough for also private
homepages.</p>

<p>Black Cat CMS is easily installed and started, and can be easily adapted to fit the
needs of nearly every web appearances.</p>

<p><strong>The Black Cat CMS Installation Wizard will guide you through the
installation process.</strong></p>

